08:29.426 --> 08:31.007
But it was hard enough
for me to get in here.

08:31.136 --> 08:32.922
How are we gonna break you out?

08:33.055 --> 08:35.797
First, I need a paper clip.

08:36.225 --> 08:37.305
Second”.

08:37.434 --> 08:39.971
