08:50.823 --> 08:51.812
Where's your car?

08:51.949 --> 08:52.813
[Line ringing]

08:52.950 --> 08:54.531
Okay, they're probably
not looking for me yet,

08:54.660 --> 08:55.445
but would you ——

08:55.577 --> 08:56.657
