08:57.705 --> 08:58.820
You're not gonna ditch me,
are you?

08:58.956 --> 09:00.241
If I was gonna ditch you,
I would've done it

09:00.374 --> 09:01.910
before I had to flash
that orderly my boobs.

09:02.042 --> 09:03.657
All I said was
we needed a distraction.

09:03.794 --> 09:05.955
Well, it worked, didn't it?

09:07.923 --> 09:10.380
Okay, guys,
whenever things go sideways,

09:10.509 --> 09:12.545
one of you usually had
a good idea why.

09:12.678 --> 09:14.464
Don't fail me now.

09:15.305 --> 09:15.930
[Phone rings]

09:16.056 --> 09:17.512
Haven Harold.
Dave speaking.

09:17.641 --> 09:19.677
Thank God, final/y somebody
answered their damn phone.

09:19.810 --> 09:20.720
