09:23.313 --> 09:25.520
Duke.
Is this some kind ofjoke?

09:25.649 --> 09:27.355
Don't make me say it, Dave.

09:27.484 --> 09:29.099
Two words ——

09:30.487 --> 09:31.738
Oprah Winfrey.

09:31.864 --> 09:33.104
Duke!

09:34.199 --> 09:36.360
We all thought you were dead.
Where have you been?

09:36.493 --> 09:37.403
I've been in the barn.

09:37.536 --> 09:39.822
lt spit me out yesterday in Boston.

09:39.955 --> 09:40.910
Yesterday?

09:41.039 --> 09:43.291
