for six months, Duke.

09:43.417 --> 09:45.248
I know, but time
must move differently

09:45.377 --> 09:47.288
when you're inside the barn.

09:47.421 --> 09:48.752
Maybe ——

09:48.881 --> 09:52.294
Maybe that's why when it spits
Audrey out with new memories,

09:52.426 --> 09:53.381
