09:57.890 --> 09:59.551
I need to find her and Nathan.

09:59.683 --> 10:01.674
Now, I've been calling his cell phone,
but it's disconnected,

10:01.810 --> 10:02.845
and when I called the Haven P.D.,

10:02.978 --> 10:04.343
