10:10.360 --> 10:13.523
Dave, where is Nathan?

10:14.448 --> 10:18.817
I think I know where he is, Duke,
but he's changed.

10:20.746 --> 10:23.112
Yeah, whoo!
Come on!

10:23.248 --> 10:24.237
[Men cheering]

10:28.879 --> 10:32.747
Man, you're one crazy dude,
but yeah, definitely crazy.

10:32.883 --> 10:35.374
Cheaper than a shrink.

10:39.765 --> 10:40.925
