10:59.910 --> 11:01.366
[Sighs]

11:04.206 --> 11:06.242
Stay here.

11:06.708 --> 11:09.370
All right, hang on.
I need a break.

11:11.046 --> 11:12.877
Hey.

11:13.632 --> 11:15.168
I need a break.

11:15.300 --> 11:18.042
