11:37.656 --> 11:39.692
Yeah, well, I had other plans.

11:40.242 --> 11:41.322
Audrey?

11:41.451 --> 11:42.657
Nathan...

11:48.292 --> 11:49.657
Where is she?

11:49.793 --> 11:52.455
Where's Audrey?

11:55.924 --> 11:57.664
Hey, love, what can I get ya?

11:57.801 --> 12:00.918
—I want a screaming orgasm.
—Don't we all?

12:01.054 --> 12:02.669
—|t's a drink.
—We don't make them here.

12:02.806 --> 12:04.671
