12:06.476 --> 12:07.682
That a fact?

12:07.811 --> 12:11.520
Lexie, did you give this boy
a screaming orgasm?

12:11.648 --> 12:14.856
Well, he asked so nice,
how could I say no?

12:19.281 --> 12:22.899
After you went in the barn,
it vanished like it was never there.

12:23.035 --> 12:24.400
I made it back into town

12:24.536 --> 12:26.151
just as the last of the meteors
were coming down.

12:26.288 --> 12:27.869
It was chaos.

12:27.998 --> 12:31.331
Dave thinks you shooting Howard
disrupted the 27—year cycle.

12:31.460 --> 12:34.202
That's why the troubles didn't go away
like they were supposed to.

12:35.672 --> 12:38.584
Guard found out what I did.
They tried to kill me.

12:38.717 --> 12:40.753
Part of me wanted to let them.

12:41.386 --> 12:43.217
l was trying to save Audrey.

12:43.347 --> 12:44.553
Instead, I thought I killed her.

12:44.681 --> 12:48.720
I thought I killed you,
killed James.

12:49.645 --> 12:51.806
So what?

12:51.939 --> 12:54.601
That's your excuse for having
a six—month—long pity party ——

12:54.733 --> 12:56.519
letting people beat the crap
out of you?

12:56.652 --> 12:58.608
I needed money.
I couldn't get a real job.

12:58.737 --> 12:59.726
l have to stay off the radar.

12:59.863 --> 13:04.527
The Guard ——
If they found me, I'm dead.

13:04.660 --> 13:07.072
You got out of the barn today ——
it might have spit her out as well.

13:07.204 --> 13:08.410
Well, yeah,
I'd like to believe that too,

13:08.538 --> 13:10.199
but how come no one's
heard from her, Nathan?

13:10.332 --> 13:11.538
Barn sent you to Boston.

13:11.667 --> 13:13.874
