for all we know.

13:14.002 --> 13:16.288
You said Jennifer could hear
what happened in the barn.

13:16.421 --> 13:18.082
Maybe she can help us
narrow it down.

13:18.632 --> 13:19.747
Can we trust her?

13:19.883 --> 13:21.714
I don't know. I just met her.

13:21.843 --> 13:24.050
But she trusted me
when she didn't have to,

13:24.179 --> 13:25.419
and | get the feeling
that she needs us

13:25.555 --> 13:27.420
just as much as we need her.

13:27.557 --> 13:29.263
Do we take her back to Haven?

13:29.393 --> 13:31.224
